name: Cubelessness
description:
Only MOBILE (touchscreen)

Incredible, not "in-the-game-made-from-tutorial-and-then-build-a-lot-of-questionable-stuff-on-top-of-it" at all, one-time opportunity to create your own rhythm in the vast space!

Go forward, left or right, try not to hit your fellow cubes and become 

Master of the CUBELESSNESS!
